description	"Revan - The Prodigal Knight [Jedi Guardian]

^2Weaponry:
- Revan's Lightsaber
-- Yellow / Red / Purple / Blue Styles
-- Saber / Gun Defense (3)
-- Saber Deflect (2)

^5Force Powers:
- Jump (3)
- Push (3)
- Speed (1)
- Sense (2)
- Mind Trick (2) ^3[CS4]
- Lightning (2)
- Heal (2) ^3[CS3]

^8Attributes:
- Force Block (3)
- Force Focus (1)
- Rally

Revan-renowned as the Revanchist, dreaded as the Dark Lord of the Sith Darth Revan, and praised as the Prodigal Knight-was a Human male who played pivotal roles as both Jedi and Sith in the Mandalorian Wars and the Jedi Civil War."
